org.jruyi.common

Class ListNode<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jruyi.common.ListNode<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of the element
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, ICloseable

    public final class ListNode<E>
extends Object
implements ICloseable
    A node contains a reference to the next node and a reference to the element data. It is used to form a singly linked list.

    This class has a thread local cache mechanism for node instances.
